<div id="pf39b5" class="pf w5b h237" data-page-no="39b5"><div class="pc pc39b5 w5b h237"><div class="t m3bb xd4 h35 y2b54 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Satan are having their last chance to </div><div class="t m287 xd4 h35 y2ad9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">develop before the world, before angels </div><div class="t m613 xd4 h35 y2a92 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and men, the true principles of their </div><div class="t mfc xd4 h35 y2a89 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">attributes. The people of God are now </div><div class="t mf3d xd3 h35 y2933 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to stand as representatives of the at-</div><div class="t mf47 xd3 h35 y23bc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tributes of the Father and the Son. </div><div class="t m134c xd3 h35 y2317 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Watch therefore: for ye know not what </div><div class="t m6c4 xd3 h35 y148e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hour your Lord doth come. But know </div><div class="t m85 xd3 h35 y2d0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this, that if the goodman of the house </div><div class="t m798 xd3 h35 y760 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">had known what watch the thief would </div><div class="t m89a xd3 h35 y171b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">come, he would have watched, and </div><div class="t mbd8 xd3 h35 y2034 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">would not have suffered his house to  </div><div class="t me20 x2b h35 y2a86 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be broken up. Therefore be ye also </div><div class="t m1317 x2b h35 y2c4f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ready: for in such an hour as ye think </div><div class="t m3cf x2b h35 y2b01 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not the Son of man cometh. Who then </div><div class="t m372 x1f h35 y2a5a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is a faithful and wise servant, whom his </div><div class="t m2ff x1f h35 y236d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lord hath made ruler over his household, </div><div class="t m6b5 x1f h35 y23b2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to give them meat in due season? </div><div class="t m9a3 x1f h35 y231e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Blessed is that servant, whom his lord </div><div class="t m1721 x1f h35 y1154 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">when he cometh shall find so doing. </div><div class="t mdea x1f h35 y1155 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verily I say unto you, That he shall </div><div class="t m591 x1f h35 y761 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">make him ruler over all his goods.&quot;â€”</div><div class="t m1e5 x1f h5 y591 ff9 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Review and Herald, </div><div class="t m325 x75 h35 ye19 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">April 14, 1896. </div><div class="t md1c x195 h35 y2d18 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">101 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
